snippet.title: Berzerk Flashback
snippet.description:
RIP Flash 1996-2020

Berzerk Flashback is a collection of most of the games we've shipped on Flash in the past 13 years, fixed and recompiled for your enjoyment.

Coming to Steam February 9th 2021.

http://flashback.berzerkstudio.com
